  "text": "In Ref. [CITATION_1] scalar perturbations of the viable β 1 -β 4 model have been analysed for perfect fluid matter (i.e. matter without anisotropic stress and with adiabatic perturbations) and it has been found that they can fit the growth rate of the observed perturbations during the matter and dark energy dominated eras [CITATION_2] . In Ref. [CITATION_3] a preliminary analysis of all, scalar, vector and tensor perturbations is presented and analytic solutions in limiting regimes are found, which all do not show exponential instabilities.",
